Day 7: Added UI for To-Do App using Razor Pages

- Created Index.cshtml for UI
- Added form to insert new tasks
- Displayed list of todos using foreach loop
- Implemented delete button for each task
- Used asp-for and asp-page-handler for model binding and actions
 Index.cshtml (UI)
@page
@model IndexModel

<h2>To-Do List</h2>

<form method="post">
    <input type="text" asp-for="NewTodo.Title" placeholder="Enter task" />
    <button type="submit">Add</button>
</form>

<ul>
@foreach (var item in Model.Todos)
{
    <li>
        @item.Title
        <form method="post" asp-page-handler="Delete" asp-route-id="@item.Id" style="display:inline;">
            <button type="submit">Delete</button>
        </form>
    </li>
}
</ul>
